itemDescription: Croudace, Camilla Mary Julia (1844–1926), supporter of education for women

wikipedia_page.main: Camilla Croudace (29 January 1844 – 3 April 1926) was a British supporter of education for women serving from 1881 to 1906 as Lady Resident at Queens College London.
